NAME: Geographic Area Name
TYPOP_LABEL: Meaning of Type of operation code
RCPTOT: Sales, value of shipments, or revenue ($1,000)
VAL_PCT: Sales, value of shipments, or revenue of largest firms as percent of total sales, value of shipments, or revenue (%)
HHI: Herfindahl-Hirschman Index (based on sales, value of shipments, or revenue) (%)
RCPTOT_IMP: Range indicating percent of total sales, value of shipments, or revenue imputed
PAYANN_IMP: Range indicating percent of total annual payroll imputed
EMP_IMP: Range indicating percent of total employees imputed
